7896c467-5e8b-448b-a624-c60a8195515e	08d47f78-85c9-4672-b070-04cb012ed711	35.00	56.00	88.00	high	["hookPower", "humor", "curiosity"]	The flawless contradiction between 'never gonna give you up' and 'I'm gonna let you down' is the internet's favorite bait-and-switch phrase. This text alone reads like a toxic relationship skit, which is gold for relatable humor memes in Indonesia.	I just want to tell you how I'm feeling. Got to make you understand. Never going to give you up. I'm going to let you down. I'm going to run around and desert you. I'm going to make you say goodbye.	1	elite
46611ee8-7736-41e4-bbb9-434f9ed6ec85	3d9089cc-b816-4cb2-a4cd-ef9c72f4f36d	40.00	56.00	88.00	high	["hookPower", "humor", "relatability"]	The iconic 'Never gonna give you up' drop is an instant attention grabber. This is pure meme material that works on any platform for immediate recognition.	Got to make you understand. Never going to give you up. I'm going to let you down. I'm going to run around and desert you. I'm going to make you say goodbye.	1	elite
0b669f27-5e4f-445d-b27d-6093a37f89f9	3d9089cc-b816-4cb2-a4cd-ef9c72f4f36d	191.00	206.00	85.00	high	["hookPower", "humor", "relatability"]	Another strong chorus segment with the same viral potency. It's a classic moment that hits hard and fast, perfect for looping and remix culture.	Never going to tell a lie and hurt you. Never going to give you up. Never going to let you down. Never going to run around and desert you. Never going to make you cry. Never going to	2	elite
b293ed39-1c1f-4a00-813c-8e519b13cc69	72f4c0cd-9a9d-427c-bf47-6580d8b35e29	35.00	56.00	86.00	high	["hookPower", "humor", "curiosity"]	Builds up with 'I just want to tell you how I'm feeling' and drops into the most recognizable chorus on the internet. Instant nostalgia bait and rickroll fuel.	I just want to tell you how I'm feeling. Got to make you understand. Never going to give you up. I'm going to let you down. I'm going to run around and desert you. I'm going to make you say goodbye.	1	elite
d7b90153-cb0d-4a8d-9117-b08e5f55d791	72f4c0cd-9a9d-427c-bf47-6580d8b35e29	191.00	206.00	84.00	high	["hookPower", "humor", "curiosity"]	Full, high-energy reprise of the viral chorus. Perfect for closing out clips or riding the wave of audience recognition.	Never going to tell a lie and hurt you. Never going to give you up. Never going to let you down. Never going to run around and desert you. Never going to make you cry. Never going to	2	secondary
2b31f949-60b9-4ae5-8fa4-9a366ddb917d	72f4c0cd-9a9d-427c-bf47-6580d8b35e29	152.00	168.00	78.00	medium	["hookPower", "humor", "relatability"]	Straight into the chorus with no windup — hits the hook immediately. Great for punchy edits and TikTok transitions.	it. I just want to tell you how I'm feeling. Got to make you understand. Never going to give you up. Never going to let you down. Never going to run around and desert	3	secondary
c44ff09e-0afc-457d-9f2b-7428cef821cc	9cb40b70-71f0-4a57-acba-0afb0e3c6e85	40.00	56.00	95.00	high	["hookPower", "humor", "relatability"]	This is the iconic chorus that hooks instantly with the first line. The 'Never gonna give you up' promise is immediately recognizable and meme-worthy, which drives high engagement.	Got to make you understand. Never going to give you up. I'm going to let you down. I'm going to run around and desert you. I'm going to make you say goodbye.	1	elite
faca2013-3424-4f3c-8039-fac21026fb06	799d84f5-7152-41dc-b6ef-08258d3ac2d5	191.00	206.00	80.00	high	["hookPower", "emotion", "motivation"]	The 'Never gonna give you up' promise starts with a strong negative hook that grabs attention instantly, and the theme of unwavering commitment is both emotional and motivational for a wide audience.	Never going to tell a lie and hurt you. Never going to give you up. Never going to let you down. Never going to run around and desert you. Never going to make you cry. Never going to	1	secondary
fb19c27b-e953-4939-9d01-12813b44bc2f	799d84f5-7152-41dc-b6ef-08258d3ac2d5	18.00	34.00	75.00	medium	["hookPower", "emotion", "relatability"]	Opening with 'We're no strangers to love' immediately sets a relatable relationship scene and hooks viewers who connect with the classic romantic declaration.	We're no strangers to love. You know the rules and so do I. I feel commitments from what I'm thinking of. You wouldn't get this from any other guy.	2	secondary
